lown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知想點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLBJ今日係打得好辛苦<br />\n其他角色球員又唔爭氣<br />\n<br />\n不過佢都冇怨隊友 反而都時不時遞手同隊友擊掌<br />\n呢個係幾nice"},{"pid":"1098aa9898eee783ff74b62042625fcb97cf9d49","tid":267093,"uid":34273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"簡單講就係進攻死火，守唔到kd"}]}